accessibility.text: EVOLTA is not just the ultimate long lasting energy Panasonic battery; it consistently outperforms our competitors’ premium products in commonly accepted performance tests.
Panasonic launched an awareness campaign for Evolta batteries in Apr’21

Build awareness about Panasonic Evolta batteries that boast high power and last 20 times longer as compared to standard zinc carbon batteries* in high powered devices such as photo flash and toy cars.
Engaging first creative ft. brand’s mascot and brand communication, asking viewers to engage on tap.
Leading viewers to brand’s quiz centred around product’s USP of lasting 20 times longer than standard Zinc batteries.
Upon correctly answering the brand quiz, viewers are taken to a short video film made for the campaign. CTA leads viewers out to brand’s landing page.
